4 11:08:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>国会禁止 TikTok 或迫使中国剥离的新举措势头强劲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/new-push-congress-ban-tiktok-or-force-chinese-divestiture-gains-steam-2024-03-07/</link><description>美国众议院能源和商业委员会预计将于周四就立法进行投票，给予中国字节跳动六个月的时间从短视频应用 TikTok 撤资，否则将面临美国禁令。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:02:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/new-push-congress-ban-tiktok-or-force-chinese-divestiture-gains-steam-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>印度总理五年来首次访问克什米尔表示，克什米尔已经发生了变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/kashmir-has-been-transformed-indian-pm-says-first-visit-five-years-2024-03-07/</link><description>总理纳伦德拉·莫迪周四表示，喜马拉雅山地区的查谟和克什米尔地区已经发生转变，并与印度其他地区融为一体，并将这一变化归因于印度政府撤销其特殊地位的有争议的决定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 10:22:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/kashmir-has-been-transformed-indian-pm-says-first-visit-five-years-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国新疆高级官员称伊斯兰教“中国化”“不可避免”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/top-official-chinas-xinjiang-says-sinicisation-islam-inevitable-2024-03-07/</link><description>新疆共产党高级官员周四表示，北京被指控侵犯人权的中国西北部穆斯林占多数的地区的伊斯兰教“中国化”是“不可避免的”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 10:16:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/top-official-chinas-xinjiang-says-sinicisation-islam-inevitable-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>香港全速推动新安全法案，称风险“迫在眉睫”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-submit-new-national-security-bill-legislature-this-week-2024-03-07/</link><description>香港政府将于周五向立法机关提交“23条”国家安全法案，可能会进一步镇压这个前英国殖民地的异议，香港领导人李家超呼吁“全速”通过该法案。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 09:30:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-submit-new-national-security-bill-legislature-this-week-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>受制裁的油轮Liteyny Prospect停靠在中国以卸载俄罗斯石油</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/sanctioned-tanker-liteyny-prospect-docks-china-offload-russian-oil-2024-03-07/</link><description>据两位知情人士透露，受到制裁的俄罗斯油轮“Liteyny Prospect”号已停靠在河北省沧州市附近的中国黄骅港，将卸掉70万桶俄罗斯索科尔原油货物。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 08:20:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/sanctioned-tanker-liteyny-prospect-docks-china-offload-russian-oil-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>印度卢比看涨头寸达到两年多高位；路透调查：亚洲外汇空头坚守阵地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/bullish-positions-indian-rupee-over-two-year-high-asian-fx-bears-hold-ground-2024-03-07/</link><description>路透周四的一项调查显示，由于中国经济复苏的不确定性和全球货币宽松时间表拖延，印度卢比的看涨押注达到两年半以来的最高水平，而投资者对大多数亚洲货币维持看跌头寸。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:47:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/bullish-positions-indian-rupee-over-two-year-high-asian-fx-bears-hold-ground-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚总理表示，试图遏制中国只会加剧其不满</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/trying-contain-china-will-only-fuel-its-grievances-says-malaysian-pm-2024-03-07/</link><description>马来西亚总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣周四在澳大利亚发表讲话时表示，遏制中国崛起的企图只会加剧该国的局势，并在该地区制造不和。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:38:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/trying-contain-china-will-only-fuel-its-grievances-says-malaysian-pm-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>日本表示对中俄更密切的军事关系感到严重关切</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan-says-it-is-gravely-concerned-about-closer-military-ties-between-china-2024-03-07/</link><description>日本政府最高发言人周四表示，考虑到日本和该地区的安全，东京对中俄之间更密切的军事合作表示严重关切。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:24:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan-says-it-is-gravely-concerned-about-closer-military-ties-between-china-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>随着大型科技公司争先恐后地遵守欧盟规则，调查可能会发生</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/big-tech-scrambles-meet-eu-rules-investigations-seen-likely-2024-03-07/</link><description>谷歌、苹果、亚马逊、微软、Meta 和 TikTok 母公司字节跳动在过去六个月里都在努力遵守周四生效的具有里程碑意义的欧盟技术规则，从在线平台的彻底改革到后台工程。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 06:03:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/big-tech-scrambles-meet-eu-rules-investigations-seen-likely-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>立陶宛称俄罗斯可以在乌克兰继续战斗至少两年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-can-fight-ukraine-least-two-years-lithuania-says-2024-03-07/</link><description>立陶宛情报机构周四在一份报告中表示，高油价、逃避制裁和国家投资正在为俄罗斯提供足够的资源，以目前的强度在乌克兰进行至少两年的战斗。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 05:34:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-can-fight-ukraine-least-two-years-lithuania-says-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>香港法官驳回亲民主电台主持人煽动叛乱案上诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-judges-dismiss-appeal-sedition-case-pro-democracy-radio-host-2024-03-07/</link><description>周四，三名香港高等法院法官驳回了民主活动人士谭德志对其定罪和 40 个月刑期的上诉，其中包括 7 项煽动罪。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:54:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-judges-dismiss-appeal-sedition-case-pro-democracy-radio-host-2024-03-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>